Package org.uutuc.component

Class Summary
CasAnnotator_ImplBase Base class for CAS annotators which initializes itself based on annotations.
CasCollectionReader_ImplBase Base class for CAS collection readers which initializes itself based on annotations.
CasConsumer_ImplBase Base class for CAS consumers (actually a CasAnnotator_ImplBase) which initializes itself based on annotations.
JCasAnnotator_ImplBase Base class for JCas annotators which initializes itself based on annotations.
JCasCollectionReader_ImplBase Base class for JCas collection readers which initializes itself based on annotations.
JCasConsumer_ImplBase Base class for JCas consumers (actually a JCasAnnotator_ImplBase) which initializes itself based on annotations.
JCasMultiplier_ImplBase Base class for a JCas multiplier which initializes itself based on annotations.
ViewCreatorAnnotator This annotator can be placed at/near the beginning of a pipeline to ensure that a particular view is created before it is used further downstream.
ViewTextCopierAnnotator This annotator will copy the text of one view to another view.
